{"text": "A true gem for the Star Wars saga. The story of Cal Kestis is excellently delivered as themes of pain, guilt, regret and fear are explored. A likeable cast of characters accompany the protagonist on his epic journey across the Star Wars galaxy, from more well known planets like Kasshyyk, the home of the Wookies, to Dathomir, the shrouded home of Darth Maul, Savage Opress and Asajj Ventress as featured in The Clone Wars and Rebels. The Inquisitors are excellent antagonists for this story as well as the beautiful musical score, reminiscent of John Williams iconic pieces for the movies. Building Cal's skills throughout the game is immensely satisfying as you become a true Jedi. A fantastic action adventure game.", "appid": "1172380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198799322459", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "34", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594296000.0}
