{"text": "I think all or at least most people are like what the heck is this game at first, and while playing some of the routes, you ask yourself is this a joke? Well I'll tell you, it's not. This game, even though at some times it is quite humorous, has depth to it. You might not realize it, but after completing this game, you will come out a changed person. It will give some perspective as to how far a person ( or I guess a birdie) will go to keep their word. I would recommend every(birdie)one to play this, even if you think it's not your cup of tea. It's funny and it has a great plot to it, but be prepared for some plot twists. Have a nice day everyone~", "appid": "310080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198347554127", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538568000.0}
