{"text": "Kojima is a true visionary, it's almost like he peeked into the future and created this masterpiece as a foreshadow of ours. This is a story of focus, commitment and sheer will, you are humanity's beacon of hope, on a journey to make the world whole again and become the greatest delivery guy the world has ever seen. The world is incredibly beautiful, the characters will grow on you and the port is amazing, I only have a semi-decent PC and have yet to experience any problems. It's weird, unique and fun all at the same time and it's unlike anything you've ever experienced. Don't think about it and just do it, because in this world you never truly walk alone and that alone is worth the sacrifice.", "appid": "1190460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087525640", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594814400.0}
